bilingual.source: The tour takes you round the bay.
bilingual.target: 这次旅行会带你环绕海湾。

bilingual.source: This must have been the last film mum made here in the bay.
bilingual.target: 这一定是妈妈在海湾拍的最后一部电影。

bilingual.source: We had a picnic by the bay.
I like to take a walk by the bay.
The view of the bay is very beautiful.
The tern's call echoed across the bay.
bilingual.target: 燕鸥的叫声在海湾回荡。

bilingual.source: They decided to go for a swim in the bay.
There are many fishing boats near the bay.
The boat sailed smoothly across the bay.
bilingual.target: 船在海湾上平稳地航行。

list.abstract: bay是一个英语单词，有（海或湖的）湾、(尤指猎犬等)低沉地吠叫、栗色马、枣红色的等意思。
Bay，电竞选手，现为NS战队中单。 2021年6月1日，NS公布2021LCK夏季赛大名单，Bay担任中单。

yingyinNormal.en: Across the bay. Ripe fruit, his hate. Two years growing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 穿过海湾，两年的酝酿，他的憎恨已到临界点。

yingyinNormal.en: We had to build a pool to swim in the most beautiful bay in the world, the bay which has become dangerous to our health.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们只能在世界上最美的海湾里造泳池游泳，这个海湾已对我们的健康构成了威胁。

yingyinNormal.en: Kick off those heels and feel the sand between your toes at The Mirage and Mandalay Bay resorts.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在米拉奇和曼得勒海湾度假村，记着脱下鞋子，感受一下沙子。

yingyinNormal.en: Marina Bay shines like something from a science fiction blockbuster, while Gardens by the Bay shows the endless possibilities of mankind's flowering imagination.
yingyinNormal.zh: 滨海湾金沙就像科幻小说的建筑一样，触目耀眼，而滨海湾花园则展现了人类对花卉想象的无限可能性。

yingyinNormal.en: To greet the "Honu" underwater, dive in the sheltered Kahalu'u bay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要观赏水中的夏威夷绿海龟，潜入卡哈鲁乌海湾吧！

yingyinNormal.en: Ooh! Bay window! Bay window right now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哇！是凸窗！去凸窗坐坐吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Tampa Bay's got a terrible team.
yingyinNormal.zh: 坦帕湾队烂得可怕。

yingyinNormal.en: Good morning, Bay Area. I'm Natalie Boyd.
yingyinNormal.zh: 早上好，湾区，我是娜塔莉·博伊德。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, so who won? Green Bay. Detroit. What?
yingyinNormal.zh: 谁赢了？绿湾队。底特律队。什么？

yingyinNormal.en: Uniform policy for Kips Bay Creative Technology.
yingyinNormal.zh: 基普湾创新科技的着装规则

yingyinNormal.en: Or how do you deal with a good thing? How? Bay window! Bay window right now!
yingyinNormal.zh: 好运到来的时候该怎么办呢？凸窗，现在就去凸窗！

yingyinNormal.en: I'll smile. I'll smile anytime. What are we smiling about? Bay window. Bay window right now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我在笑，我一直都在笑。我们在笑什么？飘窗啊。我们去飘窗那边。

yingyinNormal.en: Take a high-speed ride with a difference, at Atlantis Dolphin Bay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在「亚特兰蒂斯海豚湾」踏上与别不同的高速之旅。

yingyinNormal.en: To the Gem of the Baltic? The Jewel of Morro Bay, California. Yes!
yingyinNormal.zh: 去芭辣湾？加州莫洛湾上的宝石。对！

yingyinNormal.en: You are a lot smarter than you look. That's what Michael Bay told me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你比看起来要聪明多了。迈克尔·贝[著名导演]也这么说我。

yingyinNormal.en: No doubt she will try. But I'm sure we'll be able to keep them at bay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 毫无疑问她会的，但是我肯定我们能拖住他们。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, oh, oh! It was something about the Jewel of Morro Bay, California.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是关于……加州莫洛湾上的宝石。

yingyinNormal.en: The Bay City Rollers for dancing. Wait, that was from my sixth grade wedding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 三重奏跳舞时用湾市摇滚（七八十年代的合唱团），等一下，那是我的六年级婚礼。

yingyinNormal.en: Guess who reported a break-in last night. Kips Bay Creative Technology. That's her.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你猜谁昨晚报告了一起入室盗窃。基普湾创新科技公司 就是她

yingyinNormal.en: I'm alone in the bay window. I've been forsaken, abandoned and a third word for alone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我可一个人在这儿坐着呢，我被遗弃了，被抛弃了，我好孤独啊。
